
force compute-oriented-bounding-box
  mount build, field gesture-utils
  mount original-points, field array-list-gesture-point

  cause call-method
    drive object, share build
    drive method, |computeOrientedBoundingBox|
    drive factor, share original-points
    throw build, field oriented-bounding-box

